snippet.title: Why Propaganda Poisons EVERYTHING - Atheist Thunderf00t Rebutted!

localized.description:
Stefan Molyneux responds to comments made by Thunderf00t in response to the recent "Defending Adam Carolla: The Young Turks Rebutted!" video involving Ana Kasparian.

Thunderf00t is an notable Atheist YouTube personality who has created many videos debunking many religious and feminist arguments. Check out his channel at: https://www.youtube.com/Thunderf00t

Comment Screenshot
http://www.fdrurl.com/thunderf00t
